Config:
	config HTOP_LMSENSORS
		bool "Compile Htop with lm-sensors support"
		depends on PACKAGE_htop
		default y
		help
			Build htop with lm-sensors support.
			This increases the binary by approx 5 kB.
			Users wanting this functionality need to
			install libsensors.
